\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{i}^{2}+\lambda_{i}^{2}=a$
\end_inset

 for all 
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

, that is, 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{i}^{2}+\lambda_{i}^{2}$
\end_inset

 is constant.
 In this case, 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
